                "url": "/topics/scheme"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/edward_mckendree_bounds_688446",
        "quote": "In all God's plans for human redemption, He proposes that men pray. The men are to pray in every place, in the church, in the closet, in the home, on sacred days and on secular days.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Edward McKendree Bounds",
            "url": "/quotes/edward_mckendree_bounds_688446"
        },
        "topics": [
