                "url": "/topics/proposes"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/edward_mckendree_bounds_688447",
        "quote": "The sanctity of prayer is needed to impregnate business. We need the spirit of Sunday carried over to Monday and continued until Saturday. But this cannot be done by prayerless men, but by men of prayer.",
